latestPosts.caption:
What an unforgettable evening of recognition and pride! 🌟 Our founder, Usha Kakade, had the honor of presenting the incredible Kapil Sharma with the prestigious ‘Entertainer of the Year’ award at the #NDTVIndianoftheYear ceremony in New Delhi.

We are proud to have been the Official Associate Partners for this spectacular event that celebrated talent and excellence!

Here’s to many more such milestones! 🏆✨

#UshaKakade #KapilSharma #IndianOfTheYear #Entertainment #NDTV #ProudMoment #UshaKakadeProductions
